#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QCheckBox, kcfg_Translucency)
#: app/config/appearancesettings.ui:92
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"Translucency requires support by the selected skin as well as your desktop "
"environment. The default skin supports translucency."
msgstr ""
"Dalinis permatomumas reikalauja, kad jį palaikytų pasirinktas "
"apipavidalinimas ir darbalaukio aplinka. Numatytasis apipavidalinimas "
"palaiko dalinį permatomumą."

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QCheckBox, kcfg_Translucency)
#: app/config/appearancesettings.ui:95
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Use skin translucency if supported"
msgstr "Naudoti dalinį apipavidalinimo permatomumą, jei palaikomas"

#. i18n: ectx: property (text), widget (QLabel, backgroundColorOpacityLabel)
#: app/config/appearancesettings.ui:126
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:spinbox"
msgid "Background color opacity:"
msgstr "Fono spalvos nepermatomumas:"

#. i18n: ectx: property (whatsThis), widget (QSpinBox, kcfg_BackgroundColorOpacity)
#: app/config/appearancesettings.ui:136
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:whatsthis"
msgid ""
"When using translucency, the background color will be filled in using the "
"given opacity before the skin elements are painted on top of the background. "
"This allows influencing the opacity and color tint of translucent areas of "
"the skin."
msgstr ""
"Kai naudojamas dalinis permatomumas, fono spalva bus užpildyta naudojant "
"nurodytą nepermatomumą prieš apipavidalinimo elementus nupiešiant ant fono "
"viršaus. Tai leidžia daryti įtaką apipavidalinimo dalinai permatomų sričių "
"nepermatomumui ir spalvos atspalviui."

